- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper focuses on automatic controller tuning for a robotic arm, which falls under the scope of robotics.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a framework for controller tuning, which is a topic within systems and control.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses Bayesian optimization, which is a machine learning technique, to improve the controller gains.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper's use of Bayesian optimization can also be considered a form of artificial intelligence.
- cs.SD (Software Engineering): While not the main focus of the paper, the implementation of the proposed framework may involve software engineering aspects.
